{"tid":1602921,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"最新聯署 簽撚哂佢","createTime":"2019-09-29T14:27:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T22:25:50.000Z","uid":266997,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6ba9a2a169b4201ff5a21a3254ce657089cb7656","tid":1602921,"uid":266997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:27:40.000Z","msg":"【白宮聯署更新】- 27.09.2019<br />\n<br />\n請求美國承認香港為美國保護區（新）<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-admit-hong-kong-us-protectorate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpresident-trump-please-admit-hong-kong-us-protectorate&d=AXXoxpexL8qkFRpCGxAvLVpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=de7d9003\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-admit-hong-kong-us-protectorate</a><br />\n<br />\n請美國政府行使《全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法》，制裁親中人士。(10/10到期）<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/global-magnitsky-act-pro-beijing-officials-hong-kong-executive-council\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fglobal-magnitsky-act-pro-beijing-officials-hong-kong-executive-council&d=AXXoxpexL8qkFRpCGxAvLVpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=cfb21464\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/global-magnitsky-act-pro-beijing-officials-hong-kong-executive-council</a><br />\n<br />\n聯署請求美國拯救香港巿民，作人道救援（10/11到期）<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-us-armed-force-hong-kong-rescue-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-force\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-send-us-armed-force-hong-kong-rescue-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-force&d=AXXoxpexL8qkFRpCGxAvLVpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=75a0bbb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-us-armed-force-hong-kong-rescue-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-force</a><br />\n<br />\n請美國國會禁止香港警察移民或入境美國（10/18到期）<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-impose-sanctions-hong-kong-police-until-all-have-committed-state-terrorism-crimes-are-brought-justice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-impose-sanctions-hong-kong-police-until-all-have-committed-state-terrorism-crimes-are-brought-justice&d=AXXoxpexL8qkFRpCGxAvLVpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=f03e0d38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-impose-sanctions-hong-kong-police-until-all-have-committed-state-terrorism-crimes-are-brought-justice</a><br />\n<br />\n請美國通過《保護香港法》，停止向港發售人群控制裝備<br />\n（10/14到期）<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hongkongers-urge-congress-pass-protect-hong-kong-act\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhongkongers-urge-congress-pass-protect-hong-kong-act&d=AXXoxpexL8qkFRpCGxAvLVpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=afd9f3b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hongkongers-urge-congress-pass-protect-hong-kong-act</a><br />\n<br />\n制裁梁振英禁足到美國或歐洲，凍結海外資產，因他提出用賞金方式捕捉香港抗爭者，使香港進入更激烈的分裂。<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/zhi-cai-liang-zhen-ying-jin-zu-dao-mei-guo-huo-ou-zhou-dong-jie-hai-wai-zi-chan-yin-ta-ti-chu-yong-shang-jin-fang-shi-bu-zhuo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fzhi-cai-liang-zhen-ying-jin-zu-dao-mei-guo-huo-ou-zhou-dong-jie-hai-wai-zi-chan-yin-ta-ti-chu-yong-shang-jin-fang-shi-bu-zhuo&d=AXXoxpexL8qkFRpCGxAvLVpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=30b14772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/zhi-cai-liang-zhen-ying-jin-zu-dao-mei-guo-huo-ou-zhou-dong-jie-hai-wai-zi-chan-yin-ta-ti-chu-yong-shang-jin-fang-shi-bu-zhuo</a>"},{"